parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the electric power steering can cause the steering wheel to lock up, making it difficult or impossible to control the vehicle, which can lead to accidents or loss of control.
symptoms: The power steering assist fault message is displayed
the steering wheel becomes hard to turn
the steering wheel locks up
the vehicle is difficult to control
the power steering assist fault warning light is illuminated.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the electronic throttle body can cause the vehicle to lose power, stall, or hesitate while driving, which can lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: The vehicle loses power
stalls
or hesitates while driving
the check engine light and wrench symbol light illuminate
the vehicle shakes or jerks while driving.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The transmission issues can cause the vehicle to hesitate, jerk, or lose power while driving, which can lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded.

jerks
or loses power while driving

stalls

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the throttle body can cause the vehicle to stall or lose power, leading to a loss of control and increasing the risk of accidents.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The sudden acceleration of the vehicle can cause the driver to lose control, leading to accidents or near-misses.

the brake pedal may not respond

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the rear brake/tail lights can cause other drivers to be unaware of the vehicle's braking, increasing the risk of rear-end collisions.
symptoms: The brake lights stay on constantly
the brake lights do not come on when the brake pedal is pressed
the tail lights flicker or do not work at all
the brake lights are dim or not as bright as the other side.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the brake lights to function properly when the headlights are on can cause other drivers to be unaware of the vehicle's braking, increasing the risk of rear-end collisions.
symptoms: The brake lights stay on constantly when the headlights are on
the brake lights do not come on when the brake pedal is pressed when the headlights are on
the tail lights flicker or do not work at all when the headlights are on.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the LED light assembly can cause the brake lights to malfunction, increasing the risk of rear-end collisions.
symptoms: The LED lights in the brake light assembly fail
the entire brake light assembly needs to be replaced
the replacement cost is high.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the airbag to deploy in a crash can result in serious injury or death.
symptoms: The airbag warning light is illuminated
the airbag does not deploy in a crash
the vehicle is involved in a crash and the airbag does not deploy.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Delayed or Unavailable Airbag Replacement Parts
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The delay or unavailability of airbag replacement parts can leave vehicles with defective airbags on the road, putting drivers and passengers at risk of serious injury or death.
symptoms: The dealer is unable to obtain the necessary parts to repair the airbag
the manufacturer is unable to provide a timeline for part availability
the vehicle is unable to be repaired due to part unavailability.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Poor service from dealerships can lead to frustration and delay in repairing defective airbags, putting drivers and passengers at risk of serious injury or death.
symptoms: The dealer is unresponsive or unhelpful
the dealer is unable to provide a loaner vehicle
the dealer is unwilling to repair the vehicle in a timely manner.
